		<p>Hmm.  Now how do we upgrade from one computer to another without losing the backup history?</p>

		<div class="reply">
			<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2008/09/07/a-bigger-timemachine-without-changing-history/?replytocom=749#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-749", "749", "respond", "454")'>Reply</a>		</div>
