		<p>Worked perfectly. As several have noted, Step 7 is the key. It&#8217;s not intuitive; in fact, it&#8217;s counter-intuitive.  Instead of reformatting the old drive, however, it&#8217;s found a new home in our safe deposit box with more than three years of personal and professional records. Now I&#8217;m comfortable with deleting material that I was keeping only for archival purposes.</p>

		<div class="reply">
			<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2008/09/07/a-bigger-timemachine-without-changing-history/?replytocom=834#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-834", "834", "respond", "454")'>Reply</a>		</div>
