			Tuesday 2010-07-13 at 03:50 \3\Jul\UTC +0000</a>		</div>

		<p>I think I have the solution. I had two Terminal windows open after having done a &#8220;cd&#8221; to each of the volumes. They therefore couldn&#8217;t be ejected.</p>
<p>In both windows I did &#8220;cd /&#8221; and re-executed the procedure. The process is currently proceeding, after both volumes were unmounted.</p>

